T02TD3769E:140b-23: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la phyag byas nas bskor ba byas te langs nas khyed kyis zhes bya ba la sogs pa dang /
T02TD3769E:140b-24: ngo mtshar gyi phyag rgyas btab la rang gi lha'i nga rgyal gyis spyod lam rnam bzhi'i sgo nas ji ltar 'dod pas gnas par bya'o //
T02TD3769E:140b-25: de ni bgegs rab tu zhi bar byed pa'i gtor ma'i cho ga'o /
T02TD3769E:140b-27: // / gdon dang phyogs skyong tshim bya'i phyir //
T02TD3769E:140b-28: dpung bzangs rgyud las ji skad gsungs //
T02TD3769E:140b-29: gtor ma'i las ni lung bzhin du //
T02TD3769E:140b-30: de nas dang por rab bshad bya //
T02TD3769E:141a-1: por sngar bshad pa'i bza' ba dang bca' ba la sogs pa nye bar bsogs te cha gnyis su byas nas cha gcig la gdon rnams tshim par bya ba'i phyir tshigs su bcad pa 'di rnams brjod par bya'o //
T02TD3769E:141a-2: lha dang lha min gnod sbyin lto 'phye grul //
T02TD3769E:141a-3: nam mkha' lding dang 'dab bzang lus srul po //
T02TD3769E:141a-4: dri za srin po gdon gyi rigs rnams dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-5: gang dag sa la gnas pa'i rdzu 'phrul can //
T02TD3769E:141a-6: bdag cag pus mo sa la btsugs nas ni //
T02TD3769E:141a-7: thal sbyar khyed rnams la yang gsol 'de bas na //
T02TD3769E:141a-8: bu smad bcas shing g-yog 'khor bcas pa rnams //
T02TD3769E:141a-9: gsan nas phan 'dogs slad du 'dir sbyon cig /'byung po gang dag ri rab steng gnas dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-10: dga' ba'i tshal dang lha yul kun gnas dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-11: shar nub ri dang nyi zla'i khyim rnams dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-12: grong khyer kun na gang dag gnas pa dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-13: chu bo kun dang chu bo'i ngogs rnams dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-14: rin chen gnas na lhag par gang gnas dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-15: rdzing dang mtsho dang lu ma lteng ka dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-16: khron pa dang ni ngam grog chu mig dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-17: grong dang phyugs lhas dang ni nags tshal dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-18: khang stong dang ni lha yi khang pa dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-19: gang dag gtsug lag khang dang mchod rten gnas //
T02TD3769E:141a-20: so nam khyim dang glang po'i khang rnams dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-21: gang dag rgyal po'i dkor khang gnas pa dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-22: srang dang khyams dang grong dang 'dun sa dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-23: gang dag shing gcig drung dang lam chen gnas //
T02TD3769E:141a-24: dur khrod dang ni nags tshal che gnas dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-25: seng ge glang chen dred kyi gnas rnams dang ;
T02TD3769E:141a-26: /'jigs su rung ba'i dgon pa che gnas dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-27: chu gling mchog dag tu ni gnas bcas dang //
T02TD3769E:141a-28: gang dag 'brog dgon dur khrod gnas na gnas //
T02TD3769E:141a-29: dga' zhing mgu nas dri dang me tog phreng //
T02TD3769E:141a-30: spos dang me tog mar me gus phul ba //
T02TD3769E:141a-31: 'di dag bsnams te so sor bzhes nas kyang //
T02TD3769E:141a-32: las 'di dag gi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
T02TD3769E:141a-33: gdon la mchod pa bya ba'i phyir de ltar bya ste /
T02TD3769E:141a-34: de nas cha gcig la phyogs skyong rnams la mchod par bya ba'i phyir tshigs su bcad pa 'di rnams brjod par bya'o //
T02TD3769E:141b-0: shar phyogs rdo rje can @141b te lha tshogs bcas //
T02TD3769E:141b-1: gtor ma phul ba 'di dag bzhes su gsol //
T02TD3769E:141b-2: me dang gshin rje bden bral srin po'i bdag / chu bdag rlung bdag nor gyi bdag po dang //
T02TD3769E:141b-3: steng gi nyi zla tshangs pa chen po dang //
T02TD3769E:141b-4: lha rnams ma lus sa yi klu dag dang //
T02TD3769E:141b-5: ri yi lha dang gsang ba'i tshogs 'dus la //
T02TD3769E:141b-6: so so so sor gtor ma phul ba rnams //
T02TD3769E:141b-7: rang rang gi ni phyogs su bzhugs nas kyang //
T02TD3769E:141b-8: rang gi bu smad grogs dang g-yog 'khor bcas //
T02TD3769E:141b-9: dpung dang sde bcas mnyes nas bzhes su gsol //
T02TD3769E:141b-10: spos dang me tog gtor ma lha bshos ni //
T02TD3769E:141b-11: 'di dag bzhes shing so sor bsnams nas kyang //
T02TD3769E:141b-12: bya ba 'di ni 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
T02TD3769E:141b-13: 'di ni bgegs nye bar zhi bar byed pa'i don du'am /
T02TD3769E:141b-14: dgos pa gzhan 'dod pa'i mkhas pa rnams kyis bsgrub par bya'o //
T02TD3769E:141b-15: gtor ma 'di la sngags rnams ni //
T02TD3769E:141b-16: kun du 'byung ba med mod kyi //
T02TD3769E:141b-17: 'on kyang tshigs bcad tsam gyis ni //
T02TD3769E:141b-19: dka' thub mthu dang bden pa rnams //
T02TD3769E:141b-20: lhag par yang dag thob 'gyur ba //
T02TD3769E:141b-21: bcom ldan 'das kyi bka' lung ni //
T02TD3769E:141b-23: slu ba med pa'i tshig gang yin //
T02TD3769E:141b-24: de ni gsang sngags nyid du 'dod //
T02TD3769E:141b-25: mu stegs kyis ni bstan pa'i sngags //
T02TD3769E:141b-26: de nyid phyir na chad ma min //
T02TD3769E:141b-27: de bas dngos grub thob rnams kyi //
T02TD3769E:141b-28: tshig gang de sngags nyid yin te //
T02TD3769E:141b-29: spyod lam bzhi po de dag ni //
T02TD3769E:141b-30: phyag rgya nyid du bshad pa yin //
T02TD3769E:141b-31: de bas gtor ma'i las 'di la //
T02TD3769E:141b-32: tshigs bcad gsang sngags nyid du 'grub //
T02TD3769E:141b-33: de bas 'dir ni sv'a h'a sogs //
T02TD3769E:141b-34: spel ba'i sngags ni dgos pa med //
T02TD3769E:141b-35: de ni gdon dang phyogs skyong rnams kyi gtor ma'i cho ga'o /
T02TD3769E:141b-37: // / dkyil 'khor thams cad tshim bya'i phyir //
T02TD3769E:141b-38: dus kyi 'khor lo las gsungs pa //
T02TD3769E:141b-39: gtor ma'i las ni shin tu gsang //
T02TD3769E:141b-40: de bzhen gshegs dang lha mo rnams //
T02TD3769E:141b-42: khro bo mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis //
T02TD3769E:141b-43: sum cu drug gi bar gsal bar //
T02TD3769E:141b-44: de nas gzhan yang rab bshad bya //
T02TD3769E:141b-45: dang po sbyor ba sogs dbye bas //
T02TD3769E:141b-47: de yi mtha' mar rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD3769E:142a-2: ye shes 'khor lo rang snying nas //
T02TD3769E:142a-3: sna yi bu ga g-yas dang g-yon //
T02TD3769E:142a-4: gnyis nas kun du spro bya zhing //
T02TD3769E:142a-5: dkyil 'khor la ni yang dag dgod //
T02TD3769E:142a-6: chos kyi 'khor lo'i phyogs kyi mtha' //
T02TD3769E:142a-7: bzhi po las kyang mkha' 'gro sogs //
T02TD3769E:142a-8: gnas ni nyi shu rtsa bzhi las //
T02TD3769E:142a-9: rab tu gtum mo la sogs spro //
T02TD3769E:142a-10: khva yi gdong can la sogs pa //
T02TD3769E:142a-11: thams cad za byed mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD3769E:142a-12: rul ba'i dri ldan la sogs sgo //
T02TD3769E:142a-13: dur khrod rnams nas yang dag spro //
T02TD3769E:142a-15: mkha' 'gro ma yi dkyil 'khor mchog / mthong nas mchod yon zhabs bsil sogs //
T02TD3769E:142a-16: sngar bzhin rnal 'byor so sor dbul //
T02TD3769E:142a-17: de nas sngar bzhin chu skyes sogs //
T02TD3769E:142a-18: rnal 'byor pas ni rnam par bsam //
T02TD3769E:142a-19: bdud rtsi lnga yang bsam par bya //
T02TD3769E:142a-20: rang gi sa bon byin brlabs shing //
T02TD3769E:142a-22: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin du //
T02TD3769E:142a-23: de dag brtul zhugs chen pos bsam //
T02TD3769E:142a-24: de nas rnam par sbyang ba la sogs pa'i sngags kyi tshig ni 'di rnams yin no //
T02TD3769E:142a-25: aom na ma:shr'i badzra d'a ki ya aom a'a:h'um /
T02TD3769E:142a-26: yi ge aom gyis sbyang bar bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142a-27: yi ge a'a:yis spel bar bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142a-28: yi ge h'um gis bdud rtsir bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142a-29: lag pa g-yon pas sbyang bar bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142a-30: lag pa g-yas pas rtogs par bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142a-31: thal mo bkab nas spar bar bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142a-32: nam mkha' lding gi phyag rgyas zla bzhu ba'i rang bzhin du bdud rtsir bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142a-33: de nas g-yon pa'i srin lag gis dbus nas thig le blangs te sa la chos 'byung gru gsum bya zhing ;
T02TD3769E:142a-34: de'i nang du zlum po'i thig le'i gzugs can bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142a-35: de'i nang du me long gi gzugs brnyan bzhin du gsal ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsam zhing de tshim par bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142a-41: li l'i zhes bya ba ni rnam par shes pa la sogs pa'i phung po rnams dang nam mkha' la sogs pa'i khams rnams so //
T02TD3769E:142a-48: aom a'a:h'um zhes bya ba ni dbang po drug go //
T02TD3769E:142a-53: ha h'a zhes bya ba ni thabs dang shes rab kyi sku can gyi khro bo bcu dang /
T02TD3769E:142b-0: las kyi dbang po dang zhe sdang rdo rje la @142b sogs pa'i bdag nyid can dag go //
T02TD3769E:142b-1: ka k'a kha kh'a ga g'a gha gh'a nga ng'a /
T02TD3769E:142b-2: tsa ts'a tsha tsh'a dza dz'a dzha dzh'a nya ny'a /
T02TD3769E:142b-3: ta t'a tha th'a da d'a dha dh'a na n'a /
T02TD3769E:142b-4: pa p'a pha ph'a ba b'a bha bh'a ma m'a /
T02TD3769E:142b-5: ta t'a tha th'a da d'a dha dh'a na n'a /
T02TD3769E:142b-6: sha sh'a sha sh'a sa s'a ha h'a tshya tshy'a ha h'a /
T02TD3769E:142b-7: ya y'a ra r'a wa w'a la l'a ksha ksh'a zhes bya ba ni thabs dang shes rab kyi rigs sum cu rtsa drug tshim par bya ba'i cho ga'i sngags so //
T02TD3769E:142b-8: de ltar brjod nas dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo'i mkha' 'gro ma tshim par bya ba'i phyir srin lag dang mthe bong dag gis thig le phul te /
T02TD3769E:142b-9: dkyil 'khor rang gi yan lag la bsdu bar byas nas /
T02TD3769E:142b-10: rang gi kha mtshan ma gcig par bdud rtsi lnga'i thig le mkha' 'gro ma'i grangs dang mnyam pa sngags 'di sa gtor bar bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142b-11: aom sarba kro dha d'a ka n+ya ai mam ba lim pra t'i tstshantu sa ma ya ma nu sma ra a'a:h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3769E:142b-12: de nas yongs su mnyes par bya ba'i don du yang sngags 'di brjod par bya ste /
T02TD3769E:142b-13: aom di by'an ne sa m'a dhi dhya na pri na ne sv'a h'a /
T02TD3769E:142b-14: de'i rjes la mkha' 'gro ma'i 'khor lo ma lus pa yongs su mnyes par gyur nas khams gsum pa yang de kho na bzhin du bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142b-15: de nas langs te ye shes kyi 'khor lo gshegs su gsol ba /
T02TD3769E:142b-16: dam tshig gi 'khor lo nang du bcug ste /
T02TD3769E:142b-17: smon lam btab la bsod nams yongs su bsngos te /
T02TD3769E:142b-18: rang gi lha'i nga rgyal du dmigs la snang ba tsam gyis rang gi ngo bo'i spyod lam rnams kyis gnas par bya'o //
T02TD3769E:142b-19: de ni dus kyi 'khor lo'i man ngag gi rim pa'i rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi gtor ma'i cho ga'o /
T02TD3769E:142b-21: // / gang gi lus ni rab rgyas shing //
T02TD3769E:142b-22: bde ba chen po thob 'gyur ba //
T02TD3769E:142b-23: yi dags tshim byed gtor ma ni //
T02TD3769E:142b-24: de nas gzhan yang rab bshad bya //
T02TD3769E:142b-25: dang po chu ni drag zug pa'i //
T02TD3769E:142b-26: chu bo nub bltas song nas ni //
T02TD3769E:142b-27: lag pa la sogs bkrus nas ni //
T02TD3769E:142b-28: gus pa yis ni bzlas par bya //
T02TD3769E:142b-29: padma'i phreng ba blangs nas ni //
T02TD3769E:142b-30: mkhas pas brgya dang rtsa brgyad bzlas //
T02TD3769E:142b-31: sngags ni yi ge drug pa ste //
T02TD3769E:142b-32: dngos su 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs //
T02TD3769E:142b-33: aom dang ma ni padme dang //
T02TD3769E:142b-34: h'um gi mtha' can sngags rgyal po //
T02TD3769E:142b-35: yi dags rnams kyi bkres skom sogs //
T02TD3769E:142b-36: nyon mongs gdung ba 'dzoms byed pa //
T02TD3769E:142b-38: zhi ba 'phags pa spyan ras gzigs //
T02TD3769E:143a-2: zhal gcig phyag ni gnyis pa ste //
T02TD3769E:143a-3: mchog sbyin chu skyes dag gis mtshan /
T02TD3769E:143a-4: thugs rje'i rang gi shugs kyis ni //
T02TD3769E:143a-5: gdung par 'gyur ba'i yid mnga' ba //
T02TD3769E:143a-6: mtsho skyes chen po'i ge sar gyi //
T02TD3769E:143a-7: lte ba'i dbus na yang dag bzhugs //
T02TD3769E:143a-8: skyil krung phyed par bzhugs gyur pa //
T02TD3769E:143a-9: 'od dpag med pas dbu rgyan byas //
T02TD3769E:143a-10: zla ba'i 'od kyis brgyan gyur cing //
T02TD3769E:143a-12: sdug bsngal gsum gyis sdug bsngal gyur //
T02TD3769E:143a-13: ma lus 'gro ba skyob brtson pa //
T02TD3769E:143a-14: rnal 'byor pas ni bdag nyid bsam //
T02TD3769E:143a-15: skrag 'gyur ri dags gzhon nu ma'i //
T02TD3769E:143a-16: g-yo ba'i mig ni zil gnon mdzad //
T02TD3769E:143a-17: yid 'ong lha mo sgrol ma ni //
T02TD3769E:143a-18: g-yas logs su ni bsgom bar bya //
T02TD3769E:143a-19: g-yon du de bzhin ser por snang //
T02TD3769E:143a-20: phyag byed pa la yang dag brtson //
T02TD3769E:143a-21: zla ba phyed pa dang mtshungs pa'i //
T02TD3769E:143a-22: dpral ba dang ldan khro gnyer can //
T02TD3769E:143a-23: de nas snying gi'i pad dbus su //
T02TD3769E:143a-24: yi ge hr'i:ni yang dag bsam //
T02TD3769E:143a-26: gsal bar byas nas rab tu dgang //
T02TD3769E:143a-27: 'od zer mang po de nyid kyis //
T02TD3769E:143a-28: shin tu skem pa'i yi dags ltar //
T02TD3769E:143a-29: rang gi skra dang ba sbus g-yogs //
T02TD3769E:143a-30: gsus pa ri bo dag dang mtshungs //
T02TD3769E:143a-31: mgrin pa'i wa las byung ba yi //
T02TD3769E:143a-33: rus pa snabs lud bkres zas nyen //
T02TD3769E:143a-34: rang gi mchu dang lkog ma rnams //
T02TD3769E:143a-35: de rnams bltas nas bsod ldan pas //
T02TD3769E:143a-36: snying rje chen po bskyed byas nas //
T02TD3769E:143a-37: de rnams steng du lus byung ba'i //
T02TD3769E:143a-39: de nas snying rje'i shugs kyis ni //
T02TD3769E:143a-40: lag pa dag las shin tu byung //
T02TD3769E:143a-41: 'o ma'i rgyun gyi de dag ni //
T02TD3769E:143a-42: snyim ba kha dang 'brel ba dgang //
T02TD3769E:143a-43: de nas lo ma 'bras chan dang //
T02TD3769E:143a-44: 'o ma dang ni mngar gsum gyis //
T02TD3769E:143a-45: snod ni shin tu gang byas nas //
T02TD3769E:143a-46: de rnams 'di ltar bod par bya //
T02TD3769E:143a-47: aom a'a yantu a'a yantu ma h'a pre ta sanggha shushka ma kanthosh'a p'u ta /
T02TD3769E:143a-48: ksha d'i p'a s'a wa shr'i kri ta dhi ni tsi tta /
T02TD3769E:143a-49: ai mam ba lim gri hna ta dzi gha tha bi ba tha bh'unydza tha su khawa tyam ra ma tha /
T02TD3769E:143a-50: pu nar ku shal dhi ma ra tha sv'a h'a /
T02TD3769E:143a-51: sngags 'di yis ni yi dags kyi //
T02TD3769E:143a-52: rigs chen po la de nas ni //
T02TD3769E:143a-53: gtor ma sbyin phyir sngags 'di ni //
T02TD3769E:143a-54: rnal 'byor pa ni gsal bar brjod //
T02TD3769E:143b-0: aom na mo bha ga ba te aa pa ya bhi ru ka te dzo r'a dz'a ya ta th'a ga ta ya aarha te samyakasam @143b buddh'a ya /
T02TD3769E:143b-2: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta aa ba lo ki te /
T02TD3769E:143b-5: h'um dzdza sarba pre ta ka la ni santarpa ni sv'a h'a /
T02TD3769E:143b-6: de nyid kyi phyag rgya 'byung ste lag pa gnyis kyis thal mo kha cung zad phye ba byas la mdzub mo dag rna cha'i rnam par byas pa'i phyag rgya byas te /
T02TD3769E:143b-7: yi dags kyi gtor ma'i sngags dang phyag rgya'o /
T02TD3769E:143b-8: de nas chu bo de nyid 'o mar 'brub par bsams la de nyid du gtor ma de dor bar bya'o //
T02TD3769E:143b-9: yi dags de rnams kyang lus yongs su rgyas pa 'od zer gyi tshogs de nyid kyi steng du bteg la /
T02TD3769E:143b-10: bde ba can gyi 'jig rten gyi khams 'jig rten dbang phyug bzhin du padma'i stan la nye bar gnas pa bsam gtan la dga' ba'i yid can du bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3769E:143b-11: de ni yi dags kyi gtor ma'o /
T02TD3769E:143b-13: // / bdag nyid skal bzang sgrub pa dang //
T02TD3769E:143b-14: rgyal po la sogs dbang bya'i phyir //
T02TD3769E:143b-15: dri za'i gtor ma bsgrub pa ni //
T02TD3769E:143b-16: de nas gtor ma rab bshad bya //
T02TD3769E:143b-24: ba la la sogs pa rnams kyis nye bar byugs la dbus kyi gnas su aa ka ru'i spos dud sna tshogs kyi dri bsrung yid du 'ong ba /
T02TD3769E:143b-25: nor bu mthing shun rang bzhin can shin tu mtho ba /
T02TD3769E:143b-26: dngul dang byi ru dang gser las byas pa'i rtse mo gsum gyis nye bar mdzes pa'i gzugs can dri zi'i rgyal po rnams rked pa'i cha sna tshogs la sna tshogs rgyan ldan dang /
T02TD3769E:143b-27: sna tshogs mthu ldan la sogs pa dri za'i rgyal pos rnam par brgyan pa'i ri'i rgyal po spos kyi ngad ldang rnam par bsgoms la de'i steng du sngar bshad pa'i dri za'i bdag po lus rdzas dri zhim po dag gis nye bar byugs pa dra zhim po'i tshogs kyis phyogs bcur gtogs pa'i khong gang bar byas la /
T02TD3769E:143b-28: lus lha'i me tog sna tshogs kyi phreng bas rnam par brgyan pa /
T02TD3769E:143b-29: dri za'i bu mo nu ma'i ljid kyis dbyibs dgu ba la 'khyud pa las byung ba'i dga' ba dang ldan pa /
T02TD3769E:143b-30: sa 'dzin pa la sogs pa klu'i bye brag glu yongs su len pa'i sgra snyan pas lkog ma khyab pa dag rnam par bsgoms te dkyil 'khor gyi 'gram du gtor ma'i snod chu dri zhim po dang /
T02TD3769E:144a-0: @144a * // aa ka ru la sogs pa'i dri zhim po rnams kyis yongs su bkang la /
T02TD3769E:144a-7: 'bras chan dag gis gang bar bya ste /
T02TD3769E:144a-8: de rnams bod pa'i don du sngags 'di gsum brjod par bya'o //

T02TD3769E:160a-61: phan dang bde phyogs yang dag sgrub byed gtor ma'i sgrub thabs byas pa las //

T02TD3769E:160b-1: de yis deng sang skye bo mang po bde gshegs nyid ni rab thob shog / bdag kyang srid pa 'di rung ni //
T02TD3769E:160b-2: rdo rje sems dpar 'gyur par shog / ma lus bde gshegs bsam bya ba //

T02TD3769E:160b-4: rtog pa'i rlabs ni 'joms byed blo mchog skye bo ye //
T02TD3769E:160b-5: snying la rtag tu shin tu brtan par gnas par byed par shog / rgyud sna tshogs las btus pa'i gtor ma'i cho ga slob dpon dpal klu sgyur gyi zhal snga nas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
